                  <hi rendition="#i">B: III 3, 263–264, Nr. 365 (22.12.1799).</hi>
               </p>
               <lb/>
               <p>
                  <hi rendition="#i">A: III 3, 269–271, Nr. 372 (31.12.1799).</hi>
               </p>
            </div>
            <lb/>
            <div type="section">
